   <title>Kansas Conflict: Populist Versus Railroader in the 1890's, by Donald E. Press, Autumn 1977</title>
<meta name="description" content="Conflicts between Populists and the railroads were common in Kansas in the 1890's" name="keywords" content="Kansas, Kansas history, KanColl, Kansas Collection, history, Populism, railroads, 1890's, conflict, politics, quarterlies, KSHS, volunteer">
