         <blockquote align=left><font face="verdana,arial,helvetica,geneva"><b>Lt. Col. Donald E. Press is a
            graduate of the United States Military Academy, West
            Point, and has a M.A. degree in history from the
            University of Missouri-Kansas City. His present
            assignment is on the Department of Army staff at the
            Pentagon, Washington. He is also a Ph.D. candidate in
            history at George Washington University, Washington, D.
            C.</b></font></blockquote>
         
